# @node-versions: v25.9.0
# @description: Register smol_versions_native native binding in NODE_BUILTIN_BINDINGS
#
# Adds V(smol_versions_native) alongside the other smol_* bindings.
# The binding implements native semver parser + comparator + range
# matcher (replacements for npm semver's regex-driven parsing). Used
# *internally* by lib/internal/socketsecurity/versions.js as a fast
# path for the npm ecosystem; the public node:smol-versions module
# stays a JS-multi-ecosystem implementation that gates on this
# binding's availability via internalBinding().
#
# Internal-only — no realm.js patch — there's no public
# `node:smol-versions-native` shim. The companion JS module
# (node:smol-versions) provides the public surface and routes to
# this binding for the npm fast path.
#
# Sequencing: 035 anchors after 031 (smol_primordial). Insert keeps
# alphabetic order in the smol_* group: smol_primordial < smol_util
# < smol_versions_native < smol_webstreams.
#
# Files modified:
# - src/node_binding.cc: register smol_versions_native in NODE_BUILTIN_BINDINGS
#
--- a/src/node_binding.cc
+++ b/src/node_binding.cc
@@ -116,4 +116,5 @@
   V(smol_primordial)                                                           \
   V(smol_util)                                                                 \
+  V(smol_versions_native)                                                      \
   V(smol_webstreams)
